ooshmaa antaran gunank: prati ikai sataha or prati degree tapaantar par ooshmaa antaran kii dar.
ooshmaa antaran tel: vah tel jiske madhyam se ooshmaa kaa antaran hota he.
ooshmaa athwa shakti ke utpaadan se sambandhit

ooshmaa utpann karne or bhojan pakaane main hota he. yah motor eendhan or bitumen tathaa gharelu kitnashak ke villalaayak ke rup main bhi prayog kiya jaataa he. dhooma bindu tathaa shwanta iske kuch pramukh gundharm hai.
ooshmaa kaa pravesh na kar sakna
ooshmaa vinimayitra: ek garm taral se duusare thande taral main ooshmaa ke antaran ke liye prayukt ek upaskar.
ooshmaaman: padaarth ke prati ikai bhaar ke purvadahan se utpann ooshmaa kii maatra.
ooshmaayitr tel: ek kirosine prabhaaj jiskaa parishkaran vishesh rup se kiya jaataa he taaki batti par papadi na bane or ooshmaayitr main taap ko niyamit rakhaa ja sake.
ooshmiya punahsambhaavn: ek prakram jisamen ooshmaa ke prabhaav se kam octen sankhya vaale naphtha ke anvik punarvinyas se ucch apsphoterodhi gasoline banaai jaati he.
ooshmiya prakram: koi bhi parishkaran prakram jisamen bina utprerak ke ooshmaa kaa prayog kiya jaataa he.
ooshmiya maan: eendhan ke dahan se utpann ooshmaa kii sanddhantik maatra jo saamanyatya british thermal unit prati pounds athwa kilo jul prati kilo gram vyakt kii jaati he.
oosar yaa parati bhoomi ko krishi yogya banane kii bhi he.
